Package com.example.david.sdaproject

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GameDetailsAdapter.OnItemClickListener
    Parent activity will implement this method in response to click events.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DeveloperActivity
    This class presents a list of game developers and their information.
    DeveloperDetails
    DeveloperDetails represents a single game developer.
    DeveloperDetailsAdapter
    DeveloperDetailsAdapter is an ArrayAdapter that can provide the layout for each list based on a data source, which is a list of DeveloperDetails objects.
    FeedbackActivity
    This class handles feedback provided by the user and submits it to the Firebase Realtime database.
    GameActivity
    This class builds the RecyclerView and populates it with game related information.
    GameDetails
    GameDetails represents a single game entry.
    GameDetailsAdapter
    DeveloperDetailsAdapter is an adapter that can provide the layout for each list based on a data source, which is a list of GameDetails objects.
    GameDetailsAdapter.GameViewHolder
    Creates a direct reference to each of the views within a data item.
    MainActivity
    This activity is first called when application is launched.
    QuestionActivity
    This activity handles multiple radio button question.
    RegisterActivity
    This class handles the registration for new users.
    SignInActivity
    This class handles Sign in for the application.
    ViewFeedback
    This class handles the users ability to view their previous feedback on a chosen game.
    WelcomeActivity
    This class handles the different actions for the user to take.
